			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row introFooter">
			<div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">
				<a href="https://www.rijksmuseum.nl/">
					<img src="/images/RMA.png" alt="Logo of the Rijksmuseum Amsterdam" class="logos">
						<ui:attribute name="alt" description="Alt text RMA logo" />
					</img>
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-2">
				<a href="https://www.rijksmuseum.nl/">
					More information
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-1 col-md-offset-2">
				<a href="http://commit-nl.nl/">
					<img src="/images/COMMIT.png" alt="Logo of the COMMIT project" class="logos">
						<ui:attribute name="alt" description="Alt text COMMIT logo" />
					</img>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 row more-information" id="more-information">
			<h1>More information about Accurator</h1>
			<p>Accurator is developed in the context of the research project <a href="http://sealincmedia.wordpress.com/">SEALINCMedia</a></p>
